---
import PortfolioItem from '@/components/PortfolioItem.tsx'
---

<section id="portfolio" class="relative py-24 px-6 bg-muted text-foreground isolate overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 opacity-10 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_center,_rgba(0,0,0,0.2),_transparent_60%)] pointer-events-none" />

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto text-center animate-fade-up animate-duration-700">
    <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight mb-4">Work Samples</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">A few real-world projects I’ve designed and built — clean, functional, and tailored to small businesses.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-left">

      <!-- Proyecto 1: Artilate -->
      <PortfolioItem
        title="Artilate"
        description="E-commerce site for a premium artesanal chocolate brand using ethically sourced of cacao."
        imageUrl="/images/artilate.avif"
        link="https://artilate.com"
        details={`Artilate is a premium chocolate brand crafted in Alberta using ethically sourced Colombian cacao.

I designed and developed the full website experience:

• Custom UI with Astro, React, Tailwind CSS, and shadcn/ui
• Product catalog, image gallery, and an elegant About Us section
• Stripe integration for secure online payments
• Cloudflare security layer and CDN setup
• Dynamic SEO for each page and Open Graph optimization
• Weekly analytics show over 100+ page views consistently

This was a complete design-to-deploy project including brand identity and logo.`}
        client:visible
      />

      <!-- Proyecto 2: Coffee Shop -->
      <PortfolioItem
        title="Coffee Shop Demo"
        description="Landing page design for a local café. Fully responsive and minimal."
        imageUrl="/images/coffee-demo.avif"
        link="https://zippy-griffin-4f323c.netlify.app/"
        details={`A stylish and simple landing page for a fictional local coffee shop.

• Focused on brand personality and cozy atmosphere
• Includes hero section, menu showcase, and call-to-action
• Smooth scrolling and clean layout for easy navigation

Tech stack:
Astro + Tailwind CSS

Perfect for cafés, bakeries, or small local businesses looking for a modern online presence.`}
        client:visible
      />

      <!-- Proyecto 3: Healthcare -->
      <PortfolioItem
        title="Healthcare Landing"
        description="Clean and accessible site for a healthcare service."
        imageUrl="/images/healthcare-demo.avif"
        link="https://cerulean-kleicha-ab1f51.netlify.app/"
        details={`A modern and accessible landing page designed for a fictional healthcare provider.

• Strong focus on accessibility, contrast, and readability
• Clear call-to-action with trust-enhancing layout
• Ideal structure for clinics, wellness platforms, or medical services

Tech stack:
Astro + Tailwind CSS + shadcn/ui

Built to inspire trust and drive conversions for health-related businesses.`}
        client:visible
      />

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
